      "options": {
        "content": "## 🔍 Comandos de arranque\n\n**Fase 1 — gNBs (secuencial, esperar confirmación N2):**\n```bash\n# 1. srsRAN (referencia N2)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-srs up -d srsgnb_zmq\n# Esperar: gNB-N2 accepted\n\n# 2. UERANSIM gNB1 (SST=1)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-e4 up -d nr_gnb\n# Esperar: segundo gNB-N2 accepted\n\n# 3. UERANSIM gNB2 (SST=1+2)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-e4 up -d nr_gnb2\n# Verificar: amf_gnb_count == 3\n```\n\n**Fase 2 — UEs válidos:**\n```bash\ndocker compose ... up -d srsue_5g_zmq\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue     # gNB1 SST=1\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue2    # gNB2 SST=1\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue3    # gNB2 SST=2\n# Verificar: amf_ue_count == 4\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
